---

<MarketingLayout title={meta.title} description={meta.description} canonical={meta.canonical}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6" style="background-color:hsl(var(--eden-cream))">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="font-accent text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6" style="color:hsl(var(--eden-gold))">
        Eden's Table · Herb Sourcing
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6" style="color:hsl(var(--eden-bark))">
        Order Your <span class="italic">Curriculum Herbs</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="w-16 h-px mx-auto my-8" style="background-color:hsl(var(--eden-gold))"></div>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Every herb your family studies across the Eden's Table programs, gathered in one place. Each link takes
        you straight to a trusted source so you can prepare for the lessons ahead. We recommend Mountain Rose
        Herbs for organic bulk herbs, with a few sourced from Amazon.
      </p>
      <a href={BULK_HREF} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <Button variant="eden" size="xl">
          <ShoppingCart className="w-5 h-5 mr-2" /> Shop All Bulk Herbs
        </Button>
      </a>
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-6">
        Showing the <strong>Sprouts</strong> (Grades K-2) and <strong>Seedlings</strong> (Grades 3-5) herb lists, 72 herbs in all.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Herb grids: Sprouts (week order) + Seedlings (alphabetical) -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      {herbGroups.map((group) => (
        <div>
          <div class="text-center mb-10">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold" style="color:hsl(var(--eden-bark))">{group.title}</h2>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">{group.subtitle}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            {group.herbs.map((herb) => (
              <div
                class="rounded-lg p-6 border flex flex-col"
                style="border-color:hsl(var(--border));background-color:hsl(var(--eden-cream) / 0.4)"
              >
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
                  <Leaf className="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 mt-0.5" color="hsl(var(--eden-gold))" />
                  <div>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold leading-snug" style="color:hsl(var(--eden-bark))">
                      {herb.name}
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-body text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">via {sourceLabel[herb.source]}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
                  {group.programs.map((program) => (
                    <span
                      class="font-body text-[11px] tracking-wide uppercase px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border"
                      style="border-color:hsl(var(--eden-gold) / 0.4);color:hsl(var(--eden-forest));background-color:hsl(var(--eden-gold) / 0.08)"
                    >{program}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
                <a
                  href={herb.href}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="mt-auto block"
                  aria-label={`Order ${herb.name} from ${sourceLabel[herb.source]}`}
                >
                  <Button variant="eden" className="w-full">Order Now</Button>
                </a>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- One herb list, four levels -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6" style="background-color:hsl(var(--eden-forest))">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">One Herb List, Four Levels</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85)">
        The same herbs grow with your child. Sprouts and Seedlings introduce each plant gently; Cultivators
        revisits all of them in greater depth for middle school; Practitioners returns to them once more, a
        different way, for high school. Order once and you are set for years.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Affiliate disclaimer -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6" style="background-color:hsl(var(--eden-cream))">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-px mx-auto mb-6" style="background-color:hsl(var(--eden-gold))"></div>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
        This page contains affiliate links. If you purchase through them, The Eden Institute may earn a small
        commission at no additional cost to you, which helps support the development of our curriculum. As an
        Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
